** ER
E-01 INPUT PICK-UP DATE
E-02 PICK-UP DATE (YYMMDD) IS NOT RIGHT
E-03 INPUT BIN(RG CODE)
E-04 INPUT SUPPLIER
E-05 INPUT FACTORY
E-06 INPUT DOCK
E-07 INPUT ORDER NO.
E-08 CARD IS < M390 >
E-09 NO DATA CORRESPONDING IS FOUND
